The rating of this movie depends on what are you looking for on it. If you are looking for a serious horror film with good acting then this movie is definedly not for you. On those parameters one star would be generous. If you like me enjoy to have fun watching bad movies then this is a  five star most have. Also Veronica Ricci is a truly gorgeous woman,if you are buying the movie because of her you will not be dissapointed.
